                    "body": "This would be closer to `Finsupp.mem_span_iff_linearCombination` if we wrote it as\r\n```suggestion\r\n    ∃ l : ↑s →₀ (R × R), l.sum (fun yi lri => lri.1 * yi * lr.2) = x\r\n```\r\nassuming this is true!",
