                  {
                    "id": "PRRC_kwDOFcwZ1c53_c4A",
                    "body": "Here's an outline to get you started:\r\n```lean\r\nlemma mem_span_range_iff_exists_finsupp (v : ι → R) (x : R) :\r\n    x ∈ span (Set.range v) ↔ ∃ l : ι →₀ (R × R), l.sum (fun i lri => lri.1 * v i * lri.2) = x := by\r\n  constructor\r\n  · intro h\r\n    sorry\r\n  · rintro ⟨l, rfl⟩\r\n    exact finsetSum_mem _ _ _ fun i _ ↦ mul_mem_right _ _ _ (mul_mem_left _ _ _ <| subset_span <| Set.mem_range_self _)\r\n\r\nlemma mem_span_iff_exists_finsupp (s : Set R) (x : R) :\r\n    x ∈ span s ↔ ∃ l : ↑s →₀ (R × R), l.sum (fun yi lri => lri.1 * yi * lri.2) = x := by\r\n  rw [ ← mem_span_range_iff, Subtype.range_coe_subtype, Set.setOf_mem_eq]\r\n```",
                    "createdAt": "2025-03-26T00:40:23Z",
